{"tid":959883,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【華仔騷腰斬】28至30日演唱會取消　留票尾待公佈退票安排","createTime":"2018-12-29T03:22:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T04:35:52.000Z","uid":81228,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c56983002467c3b6cda1d31347e553b8f8da80ed","tid":959883,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T03:22:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181229/_2018122911045877670.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181229%2F_2018122911045877670.jpg&h=b98590c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n主辦機構宣佈取消劉德華12月28至30日的演唱會。<br />\n<br />\n劉德華昨晚因喉嚨發炎失聲，忍痛落淚宣佈取消昨晚演唱會。主辦機構決定取消12月28日、29日及30日共三場演唱會。各位觀眾保留12月28日、29日及30日演唱會完整門票，主辦機構將儘快公佈有關後續安排及退票事宜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1398618/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Flife%2Fent%2Frealtime%2F1398618%2F&d=AudTVMWvoZ5SaVOz%2Bgr6Jp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=368e90fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Flife%2Fent%2Frealtime%2F1398618%2F&h=bb56b5ad\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1398618/</a>"},{"pid":"01a6a8fc0d99406f11a151e3ff977e9bab806508","tid":959883,"uid":78791,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T03:25:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"14f6c0210f35f1a2b5b9bbedca2f17a81c164018","tid":959883,"uid":20816,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T03:26:38.000Z","msg":"捐錢俾華仔醫病啦<br />\n佢而家最需要錢"},{"pid":"442c1a32f5616786db9301b00d379f76faddf124","tid":959883,"uid":5499,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T03:29:19.000Z","msg":"拎去填海啦"},{"pid":"a4bdacf6d172543e748dcb72a9b193fcd00ccc2c","tid":959883,"uid":40089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01a6a8fc0d99406f11a151e3ff977e9bab806508","tid":959883,"uid":78791,"like":22,"disl